xt of 40:304f(3) is omitted because the complete name of the Administrator of General Services is used the first time the term appears in a section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (c)(1), the words “(including advertisement for sale, and sale)” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (d)(3), the words “as provided in paragraph (2)” are substituted for “accordingly” for clarity.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (g), the words “from time to time” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (h)(2), the words “which were enacted prior to ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1935-08-27"},"text":"August 27, 1935","children":[],"tail":"” are added for clarity."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (h)(3), the text of 40:304m(1) is omitted because ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1917-06-15/s4"},"text":"section 4 of the Act of June 15, 1917","children":[],"tail":" (22:404) was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1953-08-13/s2"},"text":"section 2 of the Act of August 13, 1953","children":[],"tail":" (ch. 434, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/67/577"},"text":"67 Stat. 577","children":[],"tail":"). In subclause (C), the words “the disposal of which” are substituted for “as” for clarity."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id80b130aa-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id80b130ab-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tai